description: The skill provides good hikes around Bay Area. It works with the invocation call "Alexa, ask Hike Master" . A sample phase to use is "Alexa, ask hike master to give me a hike that is easy"
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask hike master to find a hike that is difficult
Alexa, ask hike master to tell me a hike that is easy
Alexa, ask hike master which hikes are easy
name: HikeMaster
shortDescription: Gives List of Hikes in Bay Area
